tab-title: DJ Club @ OSU - Learn to DJ
title: Learn How to DJ
description:
There are lots of tools out there to learn how to DJ, but not all of them are great. We've put some of the most essential topics below to help get you up and running as smoothly as possible, along with some tutorials we've written ourselves.

Still confused? Feel free to ask questions in our [GroupMe](https://www.djclubosu.com/join-dj-club)
